Federal Register: 256. Tributyltin fluoride (CAS No. 001983-10-4) (FIFRA AI) (Ref. 3). Aquatic acute toxicity values for tributyltin fluoride include a bleak fish 96-hour LC sub 50 of 2.3 ppb, an algae 72-hour EC sub 50 of 9.3 ppb, and a Harpacticoid copepod 96-hour LC sub 50 of 0.8 ppb. EPA believes that there is sufficient evidence for listing tributyltin fluoride on EPCRA section 313 pursuant to EPCRA section 313(d)(2)(C) based on the available environmental toxicity data.
